    <text>
        <body>
            <div style="handwritten" type="letter">
                <head type="title">Miklós Oláh, Bartholomäus Haller and János Dubraviczky to Banská
                    Štiavnica Town Council (Kremnica, 27 March 1541)</head>
                <floatingText type="regesta">
                    <body>
                        <p>Their letter of 26 March seems to have been answered with all the recent
                            news. They thank them, and they should not change their behavior towards
                            them.</p>
                    </body>
                </floatingText>
                <pb/>
                <p>Ersam, namhafft und weyss lieb herrn und frundt, unnser frundtlich
                    dienst sein euch zuvor!</p>
                <p>Euer schreiben den XXVI. tag Martii nechst verschinen sambt den
                    aingeschlosen newen zeytungen<note type="critic">We do not know these attached
                        letters. According to a note on the outside, one of them must have referred
                        to the siege of Pest.</note> ist unns woll geantwurt, bedannckhen unns
                    derselben, haben von annder orten auch dergleichen, wo unns was zukhumbt, soll
                    euch unverhallten von unns beleiben. Sonnst was euch lieb ist, sein wir zu thun
                    willig. </p>
                <p>Datum <placeName>Cremnitz</placeName> den XXVII. tag Martii anno Domini
                        XXXXI<hi rend="super">o</hi>. </p>
                <p><seg type="signature"><add corresp="Olahus" type="insert">Nicolaus
                            Olahus custos Albensis etc.</add></seg></p>
                <p><seg type="signature"><add corresp="author" type="insert">Bartholomes
                            Haller vom Hallerstain etc.</add></seg></p>
                <p>
                    <seg type="signature"><add corresp="author" type="insert">Jonnes Dubrawichky
                            etc.</add></seg>
                </p>
                <pb/>
            </div>
            <div style="handwritten" type="verso">
                <head>On the outer side:</head>
                <p>Den namhafften, ersamen und weisen herren, richtern und rat der stat
                    Schemnitz, unnseren guetten frundten.</p>
            </div>
        </body>
